            <bug_when>2010-01-18 11:49:53 +0100</bug_when>
            <thetext>As said in bug #3332, you can always use the modelSelection to get the same as with the old value.  Take look at the following code to demonstrate it:

var rc = new qx.ui.form.RadioButtonGroup();
for (var i = 0; i &lt; 10; i++) {
  var rb = new qx.ui.form.RadioButton(&quot;r&quot; + i);
  rb.setModel(&quot;r&quot; + i);
  rc.add(rb);
}
this.getRoot().add(rc);

rc.setModelSelection([&quot;r4&quot;]);</thetext>
